<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Jorge & Alba</title>
  <meta name="description" content="La boda de Jorge y Alba · 14 de noviembre de 2026" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f4f2ee;
      --bg-soft: #ebe9e3;
      --surface: rgba(255,255,255,.84);
      --surface-strong: rgba(255,255,255,.93);
      --text: #252626;
      --muted: #67706d;
      --forest: #51615b;
      --forest-dark: #3c4a45;
      --stone: #d9ddd8;
      --champagne: #bda786;
      --line: #dde2de;
      --shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(32, 40, 38, .10);
      --radius-xl: 34px;
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --radius-md: 18px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      line-height: 1.72;
      letter-spacing: .01em;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, #fbfbf9 0%, transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #e7ebe8 0%, transparent 22%),
        var(--bg);
    }
    body.locked { overflow: hidden; }
    img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
    a { color: inherit; }
    .container { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; }

    /* -------- INVITACIÓN / SOBRE -------- */
    .gate {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 5000;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, #fcfcfa 0%, transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #e3e8e5 0%, transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f6f5f1 0%, #eceee9 100%);
      transition: opacity .9s ease, visibility .9s ease;
    }
    .gate.hidden {
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .gate-inner {
      width: min(100vw, 1500px);
      height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .gate-kicker {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: .8rem;
      letter-spacing: .34em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--forest-dark);
    }
    .gate-hint {
      margin-top: 18px;
      font-size: .96rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .envelope {
      position: relative;
      width: min(84vw, 820px);
      aspect-ratio: 1.52 / 1;
      perspective: 2200px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 34px 54px rgba(45, 56, 53, .18));
    }
    .paper-texture {
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.10), rgba(255,255,255,.10)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(70,82,78,.018) 0, rgba(70,82,78,.018) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 8px),
        repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(70,82,78,.010) 0, rgba(70,82,78,.010) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 11px);
      background-blend-mode: multiply;
    }
    .envelope-base {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(170, 173, 165, .5);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f4f3ee 0%, #e7e8e1 100%);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.7), inset 0 -18px 32px rgba(93, 103, 99, .05);
    }
    .envelope-inner-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 22px;
      box-shadow: inset 0 18px 24px rgba(255,255,255,.24), inset 0 -24px 24px rgba(78, 89, 84, .04);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .envelope-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      left: 8%; right: 8%; bottom: 10%;
      height: 74%;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(61, 71, 68, .08);
      filter: blur(12px);
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .letter {
      position: absolute;
      left: 7%; right: 7%; bottom: 10%;
      height: 74%;
      z-index: 1;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214,217,209,.96);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffefb 0%, #f8f8f4 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.08), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.88);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 32px;
      transform: translateY(14%);
      transition: transform 1.15s ease .1s, opacity .8s ease .1s;
    }
    .letter::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(70,82,78,.014) 0, rgba(70,82,78,.014) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 8px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .letter-monogram,
    .letter h2,
    .letter p { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .letter-monogram {
      font-size: .95rem;
      letter-spacing: .30em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--champagne);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .letter h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .letter p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 520px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .envelope-front { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 3; pointer-events: none; }
    .front-left, .front-right, .front-bottom { position: absolute; }
    .front-left {
      left: 0; bottom: 0; width: 50%; height: 76%;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #efefe8 0%, #ddddd3 100%);
      box-shadow: inset -8px 0 14px rgba(85,92,89,.04);
    }
    .front-right {
      right: 0; bottom: 0; width: 50%; height: 76%;
      clip-path: polygon(100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
      background: linear-gradient(225deg, #efefe8 0%, #d8d8ce 100%);
      box-shadow: inset 8px 0 14px rgba(85,92,89,.04);
    }
    .front-bottom {
      left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; height: 48%;
      clip-path: polygon(0 100%, 50% 0, 100% 100%);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e2e2d9 0%, #d1d2c7 100%);
      box-shadow: inset 0 8px 14px rgba(90,98,93,.04);
    }
    .flap-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      left: 20%; right: 20%; top: 18%;
      height: 26%;
      z-index: 4;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(87, 96, 92, .10), transparent 70%);
      filter: blur(8px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .flap {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0; right: 0; top: 0;
      height: 62%;
      z-index: 4;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 50% 100%);
      border-top-left-radius: 22px;
      border-top-right-radius: 22px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f4ef 0%, #dddcd2 100%);
      box-shadow: inset 0 -10px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.04), 0 2px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      transform-origin: top center;
      transition: transform 1.15s ease;
    }

    .seal-btn {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%; top: 48%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 106px; height: 106px;
      border: none;
      padding: 0;
      background: transparent;
      cursor: pointer;
      z-index: 6;
      transition: transform .2s ease, opacity .4s ease;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 12px rgba(56,22,18,.22));
    }
    .seal-btn:hover { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.04); }
    .wax {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 28%, #cb5b52 0%, #b73d37 22%, #922825 60%, #731816 100%);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 2px 4px rgba(255,255,255,.15),
        inset 0 -8px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.18),
        0 4px 10px rgba(72, 22, 18, .18);
      overflow: hidden;
      clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 59% 4%, 69% 2%, 78% 7%, 88% 9%, 95% 18%, 98% 28%, 100% 39%, 96% 49%, 99% 59%, 95% 69%, 92% 79%, 84% 87%, 75% 92%, 64% 96%, 54% 100%, 44% 97%, 34% 99%, 24% 94%, 15% 88%, 7% 80%, 5% 69%, 1% 59%, 4% 49%, 0% 39%, 2% 28%, 5% 18%, 12% 10%, 22% 6%, 31% 2%, 41% 5%);
    }
    .wax::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 35% 32%, rgba(255,255,255,.10), transparent 35%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 68% 72%, rgba(0,0,0,.14), transparent 38%);
      opacity: .75;
    }
    .wax::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 18%, rgba(255,255,255,.18), transparent 16%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 76% 26%, rgba(255,255,255,.08), transparent 10%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 26% 78%, rgba(0,0,0,.12), transparent 14%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 78% 78%, rgba(0,0,0,.12), transparent 14%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .wax-letters {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #f8ece2;
      font-size: 1.12rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(90, 20, 18, .4);
    }

    .gate.opening .flap { transform: rotateX(180deg); }
    .gate.opening .letter { transform: translateY(-22%); }
    .gate.opening .seal-btn {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(.8);
    }

    /* -------- WEB -------- */
    .site { opacity: 0; transition: opacity .9s ease; }
    .site.visible { opacity: 1; }

    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(245,244,240,.84);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(217,223,219,.9);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      min-height: 74px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .brand {
      font-size: .98rem;
      letter-spacing: .24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--forest-dark);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .menu {
      display: flex;
      gap: 22px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }
    .menu a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .95rem;
      transition: color .2s ease;
    }
    .menu a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 74px);
      display: grid;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 52px 0 76px;
    }
    .hero-box {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 80vh;
      border-radius: 46px;
      padding: 30px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(22,29,30,.34), rgba(39,49,48,.34)),
        linear-gradient(rgba(245,244,240,.06), rgba(245,244,240,.06)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516589178581-6cd7833ae3b2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80") center center / cover no-repeat;
    }
    .hero-card {
      width: min(760px, 100%);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 56px 30px 42px;
      border-radius: 38px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.16);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(30,40,39,.14);
    }
    .overline {
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: .74rem;
      letter-spacing: .40em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #edf2ef;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.14);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(3.8rem, 8vw, 6.9rem);
      line-height: .94;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      text-shadow: 0 3px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }
    .hero-quote {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 26px auto 8px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #f7fbf8;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }
    .hero-verse {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: .84rem;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #e3ebe7;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #fff;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }
    .hero-date {
      margin: 0 0 32px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #e7efeb;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }

    .countdown {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .count-item {
      padding: 18px 10px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.76);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.24);
    }
    .count-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 1.95rem;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--forest-dark);
    }
    .count-item span { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--muted); }

    .intro,
    .section { padding: 46px 0 18px; }

    .intro-card,
    .card,
    .timeline-item,
    .faq-item,
    .rsvp-box,
    .gallery-item {
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.64);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    .intro-card {
      max-width: 980px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.06rem;
    }
    .section-title {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4vw, 3.1rem);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .section-text {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .timeline {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 24px 24px;
    }
    .time {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--forest-dark);
    }
    .timeline-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 26px;
    }
    .card {
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .card p { margin: 7px 0; }
    .place-photo {
      width: 100%;
      height: 320px;
      object-fit: contain;
      background: #f2f4f1;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .eyeline {
      width: 78px;
      height: 1px;
      margin: 16px 0 18px;
      background: var(--line);
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: var(--forest);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: .92rem;
      transition: transform .2s ease, opacity .2s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); opacity: .95; }

    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .gallery-item {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .2s ease;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .gallery-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 340px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    .faq {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .faq-item {
      padding: 22px 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }
    .faq-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 1.03rem;
    }

    .rsvp-box {
      padding: 48px 26px;
      border-radius: 38px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.76), rgba(255,255,255,.90)), var(--bg-soft);
    }
    .rsvp-box p { margin: 8px 0; }

    .footer {
      padding: 62px 0 76px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .98rem;
    }
    .signature {
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 1.12rem;
    }

    .lightbox {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
      z-index: 2000;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.84);
    }
    .lightbox.open { display: flex; }
    .lightbox-content {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 95vw;
      max-height: 92vh;
    }
    .lightbox img {
      max-width: 95vw;
      max-height: 92vh;
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.42);
    }
    .lightbox-close {
      position: absolute;
      top: -14px; right: -14px;
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #222;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      line-height: 1;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .countdown { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .timeline-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      .nav-inner { justify-content: center; }
      .brand { display: none; }
      .menu { justify-content: center; gap: 14px; }
      .hero-card { padding: 38px 20px 34px; }
      .count-item strong { font-size: 1.6rem; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .gallery-item img { height: 300px; }
      .card, .intro-card, .timeline-item, .faq-item, .rsvp-box {
        padding-left: 18px;
        padding-right: 18px;
      }
      .seal-btn { width: 90px; height: 90px; }
      .envelope { width: 94vw; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="locked">
  <div class="gate" id="gate">
    <div class="gate-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="gate-kicker">Jorge & Alba</div>

        <div class="envelope">
          <div class="envelope-base paper-texture"></div>
          <div class="envelope-inner-shadow"></div>
          <div class="envelope-shadow"></div>

          <div class="letter">
            <div class="letter-monogram">J & A</div>
            <h2>Estás invitado</h2>
            <p>Haz clic en el sello para descubrir nuestra invitación</p>
          </div>

          <div class="envelope-front">
            <div class="front-left paper-texture"></div>
            <div class="front-right paper-texture"></div>
            <div class="front-bottom paper-texture"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="flap-shadow"></div>
          <div class="flap paper-texture"></div>

          <button class="seal-btn" id="openInvitation" aria-label="Abrir invitación">
            <div class="wax">
              <div class="wax-letters">J&amp;A</div>
            </div>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="gate-hint">Pulsa el sello de lacre</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="site" id="site">
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <div class="brand">Jorge & Alba</div>
        <div class="menu">
          <a href="#dia">El día</a>
          <a href="#lugares">Lugares</a>
          <a href="#fotos">Fotos</a>
          <a href="#alojamiento">Alojamiento</a>
          <a href="#info">Información</a>
          <a href="#rsvp">Confirmación</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero container">
      <div class="hero-box">
        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="overline">Nuestra boda</div>
          <h1>Jorge<br>& Alba</h1>
          <p class="hero-quote">“Y por encima de todo esto, el amor, que es el vínculo de la perfección.”</p>
          <p class="hero-verse">Colosenses 3:14</p>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">Nos encantaría celebrar este día con vosotros</p>
          <p class="hero-date">14 de noviembre de 2026 · 12:30 · Lleida</p>

          <div class="countdown">
            <div class="count-item"><strong id="days">0</strong><span>días</span></div>
            <div class="count-item"><strong id="hours">0</strong><span>horas</span></div>
            <div class="count-item"><strong id="minutes">0</strong><span>minutos</span></div>
            <div class="count-item"><strong id="seconds">0</strong><span>segundos</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="intro">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="intro-card">
          Después de muchos momentos compartidos, por fin llega uno de los días más especiales de nuestra vida.
          Nos hace muchísima ilusión celebrarlo con vosotros y compartir juntos cada instante.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="dia">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">El gran día</h2>
        <p class="section-text">
          Aquí encontraréis toda la información importante para acompañarnos y disfrutar de este día con nosotros.
